  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1011820/extras/96ca784cf667da28e6f30f5399a1d8f8.poster.avif?t=1567575205\" width=616 height=282 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1011820/extras/96ca784cf667da28e6f30f5399a1d8f8.webm?t=1567575205\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1011820/extras/96ca784cf667da28e6f30f5399a1d8f8.mp4?t=1567575205\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Millionaire Dancer </strong>is a rhythm game that can dance in VR.<br>Beyond simply matching the pattern, experience the feeling of dancing<br>Feel various rhythms, dance with your hands and head.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Ten songs and two or more difficulty tracks each<br></li><li> Hitbox adjustable to your body<br></li><li> Custom Track Editor(to be updated later)</li></ul><br>We are a small indie game team consisting of one programmer and two idea providers.<br>It's a lot less, but we will do our best. Thank you!",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1011820/extras/96ca784cf667da28e6f30f5399a1d8f8.poster.avif?t=1567575205\" width=616 height=282 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1011820/extras/96ca784cf667da28e6f30f5399a1d8f8.webm?t=1567575205\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1011820/extras/96ca784cf667da28e6f30f5399a1d8f8.mp4?t=1567575205\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Millionaire Dancer </strong>is a rhythm game that can dance in VR.<br>Beyond simply matching the pattern, experience the feeling of dancing<br>Feel various rhythms, dance with your hands and head.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Ten songs and two or more difficulty tracks each<br></li><li> Hitbox adjustable to your body<br></li><li> Custom Track Editor(to be updated later)</li></ul><br>We are a small indie game team consisting of one programmer and two idea providers.<br>It's a lot less, but we will do our best. Thank you!",
